item.title: Guys plz help me
item.dc:creator: @Decronix Decronix
item.description:
@Decronix wrote:

The compiler you are usign tries out several locations.
Maybe try something like this :

@echo off
Title Compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_25\bin\javac.exe” *.java
pause

Remember to change the path, to the path on your comp.
If you have JDK.1.6.0_23 change ther _25 to _23
